OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ricky Gervais has defended making jokes
OL,6, about "taboo subjects" after his new   
OL,7, Netflix special drew criticism.        
OL,9,FIn SuperNature, the stand-up comedian  
OL,10,Fmakes a string of what he describes as 
OL,11,Fironic and satirical jokes about trans 
OL,12,Fpeople, female comedians and Aids.     
OL,14,FUS LGBT rights group Glaad labelled the
OL,15,Fshow "dangerous", "anti-gay" and "anti 
OL,16,Ftrans" after its release on Tuesday.   
OL,18,FHowever, Gervais told BBC One's The One
OL,19,FShow on Tuesday that comedy is for     
OL,20,F"getting us over taboo subjects".      
